# SmartCity Ride Analytics Dashboard

## Project Overview
This project analyzes ride-hailing service data to evaluate demand patterns, revenue trends, customer satisfaction, and complaint behaviour.

## Tools Used
- Power BI
- Data Analysis
- Dashboard Reporting

## Key Areas Analysed
- Ride demand across time slots
- Revenue by vehicle type and payment method
- Customer satisfaction trends
- Complaint patterns by time and zone

## Key Insights
- Morning and evening time slots show the highest ride demand
- Luxury vehicles generate the highest revenue per ride
- Clear weather contributes to stronger ride activity and revenue
- Complaints increase more during high-demand periods and surge pricing

## Recommendations
- Improve fleet allocation during peak hours
- Maintain balanced surge pricing
- Focus on service quality in high-complaint zones
- Keep a balanced mix of vehicle types

## Outcome
This project demonstrates my ability to transform raw operational data into business insights and actionable recommendations.
